 and post consistently. Learn more by watching the video.</p></div></div></div><div class="_2srm _22s6 _3a13 _2ant"><div class="_2m2s _2m2w _2m3f _1hxe _5k7r"><div class="_5k62 _5nd9"><div class="_z7- _4ok7">2. See How to Stand Out with Good Creative </div><p class="_5tdb _4yc6" data-ms="&#123;&quot;creative&quot;:&quot;content&quot;&#125;">Wonder what qualifies as good creative on Instagram? Hint: good creative is simply good creative. It follows the same three creative principles you&#039;d apply to any marketing channel. View these principles in the video.</p></div></div><div class="_2m2s _2m2w _2m3f _1hxe"><div class="_5ne6 _22s6 _2srm"><div class="_19ae" style="max-width: 458px; max-height: 458px;"><a class="_1avb" data-ms="&#123;&quot;creative&quot;:&quot;video&quot;,&quot;creative_detail&quot;:&quot;&quot;&#125;" aria-label="Play Video" rel="async noopener" role="button" id="u_0_0" ajaxify="/v2/business/async/video/?controls=1&amp;height=458&amp;startmuted=0&amp;poster=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fgyd3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2365-6%2F15065194_117848085363426_6421882693511806976_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3Dad8a9d%26_nc_ohc%3Db262_bm5GfoAX9jVgkr%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fgyd3-1.fna%26oh%3D19b4b9daa495c1f58df1b34c51d1add0%26oe%3D5F61DC3A&amp;selector=u_0_0&amp;video_id=1068586633239755&amp;width=458&amp;loop=0" href="#"><div class="_26rb"><div class="_530- _26rg _26rc"></div><div class="_snn"></div></div><div class="_5k9a"><img class="_5k9b _5k9c _5k9b _5k9c img" src="https://scontent.fgyd3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2365-6/15065194_117848085363426_6421882693511806976_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=ad8a9d&amp;_nc_ohc=b262_bm5GfoAX9jVgkr&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fgyd3-1.fna&amp;oh=19b4b9daa495c1f58df1b34c51d1add0&amp;oe=5F61DC3A" alt="" data-ms="&#123;&quot;creative&quot;:&quot;image&quot;&#125;" /><div class="_2pke"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="_2srm _22s6 _3a13 _3d_b"><div class="_2m2s _2m2w _2m3f _1hxe"><div class="_5ne6 _22s6 _2srm"><div class="_19